list.comment:
Database - Updated properties_reservations table to make description default NULL
BackEnd - Fixed bugs in Property and Reservation controllers - Fixed SQL bugs in models - Added property, user objects to the reservation model - Added override to BaseModel->getByID for Property model
UI - Added min and max dates to moment-picker -

task.summary: - Fixed installation check - Removed footer from primary pages - Added php documentation - Import SQL file line by line to support windows machines - Fixed bugs with the renaming of `default` to `is_default` for boolean type - Added interval label to list and read view - Updated email to send user login details - Fixed bugs throughout
- Fixed state bug - Fixed issue with property intervals to add no availability - Added blank favicon to stop annoying errors
- Changed default theme - Changed default background image - Set API to LAPDI - Changed default theme in database - Fixed availability bug
- Changed theme styling for better readability
- Fixed bugs throughout - Added reservation object
- Fixed bugs with registration - Fixed bugs with minification and a misplaced comma
- Get database preferences from the same user instead of creating new, fix if time allots
- Fixed installation issue which was causing install screen to be shown for new users - Fixed trailing slashes in login and register links on welcome install page
- Placed link to reservation on properties list to book now - @TODO When Adding reservation ensure that when a reservation is booked that the time is taken from the existing property
